summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1864, for the improvement of Highland Drive, from 2nd Avenue North to 5th Avenue North, and 5th Avenue North from Highland Drive to Prescott Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing and by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, under Ordinance No. 19510 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
